        "description": "Smaller spots (50-200 μm) for fine detail/precision on fused silica surfaces; larger (200-500 μm) for broad area prep. Recommended 200 μm for balanced resolution and efficiency at 1064 nm (high reflectivity ~4% for silica). Source: Equipment specifications from Coherent and Trumpf laser systems manuals.",
