        "min": 10,
        "max": 90,
        "unit": "%",
        "value": 60,
        "description": "Ensures uniform coverage; 50-70% typical for even energy distribution on transparent/low-absorbing fused silica. Recommended 60% to minimize gaps while avoiding overexposure. Source: Process optimization studies in Lasers in Manufacturing and Materials Processing (2020)."
